From 6a67a9010f9bad06a00c181ea056e4fd41083731 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sahbot <support.opensource@softathome.com>
Date: Wed, 16 Oct 2024 15:11:17 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] UPnP/PPP: WANPPPConnection isn't advertised (HOP-7453)

Cause: WANPPPConnection services isn't implemented

Solution: Implement WANPPPConnection in xml generation
It now advertise WANPPPConnection when WAN is PPP, WANIPConnection otherwise
Implement WANPPPConnection in HTTP server to handle control

Issue: HOP-7453 - [UPnP][REG]The DUT Advertise WANIPConnection instead of WANPPPConnection [change]
GitOrigin-RevId: 812c5bdab919c59ec1972b31dfd96d639fb78899
